Children Of Morta es un juego desarrollado por Dead Mage que ya está disponible en early access y espera a su lanzamiento en consolas a partir del 15 de octubre.
Esta entrega es un juego de RPG de acción que cuenta la historia de una familia de héroes a la cual controlaremos a través de un mundo generado de manera procedural.
Tanto su estética pixel art como su jugabilidad son sus alegatos principales. Primero Contamos con un juego que trae unas animaciones extraordinarias y luego un sistema de progresión muy bien trabajado el cual se extiende hasta seis personajes que en conjunto con el combate que es divertido y equilibrado hacen de éste un juego muy entretenido.

Jeff's Instant Instagram Reviews! 
Untitled Goose Game by House House, played on the Nintendo Switch

Personal Score: 8.5/10
Score I would give when recommending to others: 8.5/10

Untitled Goose Game is the newest indie hit that everyone is talking about. It immediately had my attention when it was first announced with its simple, colorful art style and the fact that you play as a chaotic goose who just wants to ruin the lives of these townspeople. 
Gameplay consists of following a checklist of tasks to mess with these people in each of the 5 areas of the game. Then after the credits roll a new list of things to do open up for some additional mayhem. The game is very short, I finished the game and the (non time attack) extra goals in probably around 3-4 hours. That was playing leisurely. But I had a lot of fun in those 4 hours with this game, it might be short but the gameplay is very rewarding the whole time. The game left me wanting more, but not feeling disappointed by what was there, and I think that's a great thing. 
If you're on the fence about it, watch a trailer or two. What you see is exactly what you get with this game. If the trailer makes you smile or laugh, theres lots more where that came from once you take control of the chaos.

Best Friends Forever is an upcoming dating simulator and visual novel with an emphasis on dog training and dog handling. In the game, players are a new resident to New Zealand and are introduced to new people. One of the first activities is adopting a dog at the local Vet. The game introduces you to various potential dating interests, but how you train your dog will affect the outcome of who you are dating. The game features various sexual orientations as well, so if you are Gay, Bi, and so on, you can choose those options for your character. 
This was me at #paxwest in September. As you can see, they had dog seats to sit in. I really like what the team art NZ based Starcolt is doing here. They are crafting a solid series of stories here. Also, a character will have a service animal. The creative director hopes to use the game to educate others aboit service animals. 
Best Friends Forever comes out Valentine's Day 2020. Right now, it is headed for #NintendoSwitch and I believe  #Steam .

caption.text: My goal was to win a Yoshi doll, but I experienced some problems along the way. The Trendy Gamester is a Con Man and his establishment should be closed due to unethical business practices.

Bien que la souris photographe ne soit pas de la partie, ce petit moment privilégié avec Marine a été conservé pour mon plus grand plaisir 🥰🥰🥰
J’ai toujours apprécié passer du temps avec elle avant de l’amener au Village des Animaux... C’est un personnage tellement attachant que j’ai véritablement un mal fou à me séparer d’elle : j’adore son professionnalisme au Jeu dans le Vent, son enthousiasme quand on creuse des trous, ses petites leçons de morale quand on fouille dans les placards ou quand on s’attaque à une poule (même si cela l’amuse aussi au bout d’un moment 😄) et bien d’autres choses. Je pouvais rester des heures sur la place du Village des Mouettes rien que pour l’écouter chanter sa douce mélodie, espérant retarder l’échéance le plus possible.
Son rêve était aussi pur qu’elle, j’aurais souhaité qu’il existe un autre moyen de le réaliser... ✨🌊✨
.
.
.

REVIEW: BORDERLANDS 3

Borderlands 3 chega às mãos do público quase cinco anos após Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel (2014), último lançamento central da franquia com o mesmo estilo de jogabilidade. O game está disponível para Xbox One, PS4, PC (via Epic Games Store) e será lançado futuramente para Google Stadia.

O mais recente shooter looter da 2K Games e Gearbox Software traz um alívio para os fãs do gênero e da série, com conteúdo e diversão de sobra. Apesar disto, o título também incita o questionamento sobre a necessidade de amadurecimento (literal) de uma franquia prestes a completar 10 anos.

Borderlands 3 é um divertido shooter looter, com diversas opções de gameplay dependendo do seu próprio gosto, bem como uma aplausível variedade de localidades a serem exploradas, missões a serem cumpridas e armas a serem usadas. No entanto, o estúpido humor da série permanece intacto, senão retrógrado, e infelizmente descredibiliza o que poderia ter sido uma narrativa minimamente interessante com uma rasa crítica ao comportamento virtual-viciado da sociedade moderna. As tentativas de piadas são, na maioria, imbecis e irritantes. Ignorando os diálogos putrefeitos, a jogabilidade é, em geral, equilibrada e engajante apesar da repetição de fases e de inimigos. Há também muitos bugs pelo caminho, com apenas alguns danificando, de fato, a experiência de jogo.

NOTA: 70/100 - BOM

caption.text:
Avez-vous passé un bon week-end ?
Moi ? J’en ai profité pour faire une petite escapade à #Cocolint 🏝
Car, même si j’y retourne assez régulièrement, j’ai été complètement conquise par ce remake : j’avais beau me savoir en terrain connu, j’ai apprécié le fait de redécouvrir l’île sous un tout nouvel aspect et d’explorer tous ses secrets, une fois de plus 💕
En observant l’Oeuf du Poisson-Rêve depuis la Plage Coco, j’ai eu une pensée émue pour tous ceux qui ont foulés ces terres pour la première fois ces derniers jours. J’espère que vous avez vécu la plus belle de toutes vos aventures et qu’elle vous marquera profondément, comme cela fut mon cas il y a vingt-cinq ans de ça.
Au loin, le cri d’une mouette résonne dans le ciel azur, comme pour faire écho à une ancienne promesse. Le sourire aux lèvres, je sais que je ne l’ai jamais oublié... 🐚
.
.
.

caption.text:
True Rare Rating - 9.2

Limited Edition GameStop Managers Yoshi's Island DS Sweepstakes Statue. Production numbers unknown but very likely under 50 made.

In November 2006 Yoshi's Island DS was released. To reward the GameStop managers who had the most pre-orders there was a questionnaire sent out to each store that reached a specific number of pre-order sales. if the questionnaire was filled out and sent back to corporate that particular manager was put into a sweepstakes drawing for this awesome Yoshi's Island Statue.

The winners did not get them until late the following year and many of the managers who won were no longer employed for the company 😂 Those that did get them and were still around found that their shipment was commonly broken.

There have only been a dozen or so seen circulating, and many of them were broken during reshipment. This is very much a dwindling supply asset due to fragility.

Sealed copy of Yoshi's Island included for scale.
